@flint v0 hybrid

G: choose(arch)
C: team(6) ∧ deadline(4m) ∧ ship_fast
H: low_ops_capacity ⇒ prefer(modular_monolith)
P: compare(dev_speed,deploy_complexity,fault_isolation,future_split)
V: score(time_to_first_release,operability,migration_cost)
R: ! premature_distribution
A: recommend(default=modular_monolith)

[AUDIT]
Default recommendation is a modular monolith. The team is small, the deadline is short, and operational complexity is likely a bigger risk than future extraction cost.

